The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG) that has applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of deep generative neural networks as a prior is a key aspect of the paper, which falls under the category of structured inference (cs.SI).
